{"tid":2310723,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一排空凳 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-12-03T12:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T12:53:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93afffc6931ad8ecb7efbe723316037d0ee60107","tid":2310723,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201203/RM3V2H5QEZEA7GWRVIMRC32UHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201203%2FRM3V2H5QEZEA7GWRVIMRC32UHI%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=73a97f47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201203%2FRM3V2H5QEZEA7GWRVIMRC32UHI%2F&h=409e8fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201203/RM3V2H5QEZEA7GWRVIMRC32UHI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n一排空凳 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/57FWn4V_4LhM8zD782vjy3eoCfI=/5784x3856/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5K6BB35ENF6TNUFPE4UODHBDQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F57FWn4V_4LhM8zD782vjy3eoCfI%3D%2F5784x3856%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5K6BB35ENF6TNUFPE4UODHBDQ.JPG&h=f6f77e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一份遲到的施政報告，恁是再塗脂抹粉砌辭狡辯也是只贏得一片惡評如潮；主打向北看、捨近求遠、貴遠賤近的思維點題，還有什麼討論價值？怎能不令人反感厭惡？一群明目張膽只爭表忠誠的建制派議員，早已失去民心，大部份人看到的是宣傳所謂施政報告那天，立法會上可憐的場景，反對派座席只剩排排空凳，一夜之間就此消失的議員及他們的聲音，難道因此就能換來天下太平嗎？一個個無精打采、 昏昏欲睡的席上聽眾，與一排排空凳形成了可笑又諷刺的局面；不僅在香港在全世界也會淪為歷史性的笑柄，更將會是一個噩夢的開始。<br />\n<br />\n原來好打得是千方百計排除異己大開民主政制的倒車，原來權力的制衡、民主的規範是先殺人滅口，一個沒有了反對派的議會，還能是民主制度下的立法機關嗎？。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n演吧，演吧，笑劇、鬧劇。。。。。。。。"}]}